ISLAMABAD, Feb 5 (APP): Prime Minister Imran Khan Saturday expressed grief and sorrow over the sad demise of mother of Special Assistant on Social Protection and Poverty Alleviation Dr Sania Nishtar.
In a message of condolence, he prayed Allah Almighty to rest the departed soul in eternal peace and grant courage to the bereaved family to bear the loss with fortitude.
